{"tid":732724,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"比利時︰沒有想到，本以為尼馬會帶來更多麻煩","createTime":"2018-07-07T07:04:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-07T08:03:59.000Z","uid":25345,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0888590442b677a1b33f2837a9baf924537242fa","tid":732724,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T07:04:26.000Z","msg":"默尼耶︰沒有想到，本以為尼馬會帶來更多麻煩 由  oranjekitten 發表在虎撲足球‧世界杯專區 <br />\n<br />\n 比利時邊後衛默尼耶和巴西巨星尼馬是巴黎聖日耳曼的隊友。比利時和巴西的比賽前，默尼耶也坦言說不知該如何防守尼馬。<br />\n<br />\n比賽結束後，默尼耶則顯得輕鬆了很多。對於尼馬在比賽中給他製造的麻煩，默尼耶表示︰<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我沒想到，我以為會比這更加困難，但我們的防線組織得非常好。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;費萊尼和阿爾德韋雷爾德一直在幫我，我們很專注地在防尼馬，防庫蒂尼奧還有馬塞洛。我們干得非常棒。對於我們防守上的成功，我們真該自我慶祝一下。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;在進攻上，我有一些沮喪，因為我沒怎么碰到球。我為球隊做了很多犧牲，我們因此贏了球，我很開心。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n這也是比利時自1986年來第二次進入四強，他們將在准決賽中面對法蘭西，雖然默尼耶因累積黃牌停賽無法上場。"},{"pid":"d318182238bfc004f6b0355c2472fbf93582e061","tid":732724,"uid":3549,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T07:51:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i1-kknews-cc.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w1200/s/i1.kknews.cc/SIG=17gqcsc/3o050001720ssq094q20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1-kknews-cc.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw1200%2Fs%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D17gqcsc%2F3o050001720ssq094q20.jpg&h=e8af2a78&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef20f24316bce920b9d51f9c577e2da906714ae3","tid":732724,"uid":157483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T07:52:32.000Z","msg":"source? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68b3aa87fbef7be2d7e5420efe55415655a7157b","tid":732724,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T07:53:36.000Z","msg":"虎扑唔係內馬爾咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"367b